WEBVTT

00:01.280 --> 00:03.250
<i>Previously on</i>
The Handmaid's Tale...

00:03.250 --> 00:05.190
The Commander
wants to reconcile,

00:05.190 --> 00:07.080
but he doesn't know
how to do it so,

00:07.080 --> 00:08.840
I made a suggestion.

00:08.840 --> 00:10.160
Could you maybe give her

00:10.160 --> 00:11.780
a real voice?
Behind the scenes.

00:11.780 --> 00:13.500
If that would fix things.

00:13.500 --> 00:14.680
It's worth discussing.

00:14.680 --> 00:17.200
Wear the dress.
Pull the strings.

00:18.240 --> 00:20.040
Have you found her respectful?

00:20.040 --> 00:22.870
We've had trouble
with her in the past.

00:22.870 --> 00:25.040
Yes.

00:25.040 --> 00:27.340
I want to go now.

00:27.340 --> 00:29.070
All right, my love.

00:29.070 --> 00:30.860
A young girl of Hannah's age

00:30.860 --> 00:33.320
would attend a school
for domestic arts.

00:33.320 --> 00:35.240
The one in her district
is in Brookline,

00:35.240 --> 00:36.750
by the reservoir.

00:36.750 --> 00:38.940
Thank you, S...

00:39.960 --> 00:41.420
You know that man?

00:41.420 --> 00:43.320
Is it Lucas Bankole?

00:43.320 --> 00:44.700
I love you.

00:45.800 --> 00:46.870
Yes.

00:47.470 --> 00:49.400
She's gotten so big.

