We want you to blend in.

27:17.450 --> 27:19.490
Right this way,
Mrs. Waterford.

27:21.790 --> 27:23.050
<i>Attention passengers</i>

27:23.050 --> 27:25.650
<i>on Air Canada Flight 1805</i>

27:25.650 --> 27:26.660
<i>to Mexico City.</i>

27:26.660 --> 27:29.000
<i>This is the final boarding call.</i>

27:29.000 --> 27:31.000
<i>Flight 1805 will be closing</i>

27:31.000 --> 27:33.000
<i>its doors in five minutes.</i>

27:33.000 --> 27:34.240
<i>All ticketed passengers</i>

27:34.240 --> 27:36.240
<i>must board at Gate E80</i>

27:36.240 --> 27:38.090
<i>at this time.</i>

27:51.250 --> 27:52.250
I'll introduce you.

27:52.250 --> 27:54.260
No.
Not yet.

28:14.440 --> 28:16.040
Serena Waterford.

28:16.040 --> 28:18.320
Luke Bankole.

28:23.630 --> 28:24.660
Hello.

28:27.350 --> 28:28.370
I could stay.

28:30.160 --> 28:32.370
I leave that up
to Mr. Bankole.

28:35.890 --> 28:37.030
You can go.

28:38.040 --> 28:40.280
I won't be far.

28:45.240 --> 28:46.430
God bless you.

28:46.430 --> 28:48.300
Fuck you.

28:49.510 --> 28:52.150
I understand this wasn't
an easy choice for you.

28:53.470 --> 28:55.270
I thank you for making it.

28:56.650 --> 28:59.270
I did this for my wife.

29:21.440 --> 29:24.250
She's gained so much weight.

29:24.250 --> 29:26.030
She started eating solids yet?

29:26.870 --> 29:28.880
She's not a fan of the peas.

29:31.230 --> 29:32.590
Is June okay?

29:33.250 --> 29:35.320
Yes.
She's been reassigned.

29:35.320 --> 29:36.610
Where?

29:36.610 --> 29:38.060
I want a name.

29:38.060 --> 29:40.260
Your wife is
perfectly safe, Mr. Bankole.

29:40.260 --> 29:41.990
That's a lie.

29:49.500 --> 29:51.850
His name is Joseph Lawrence.

30:00.580 --> 30:02.600
I know.

30:05.240 --> 30:06.940
What do you want out of this?

30:08.220 --> 30:09.380
This visit?

30:10.330 --> 30:12.630
I just wanted
to see my daughter.

30:12.630 --> 30:13.730
She's not your daughter.

30:13.730 --> 30:15.320
Or yours.

30:16.460 --> 30:17.680
Okay, you understand

30:17.680 --> 30:18.900
this is not about biology,

30:18.900 --> 30:20.800
and I hope that you'll
explain that to her

30:20.800 --> 30:22.000
when she's old enough
to understand.

30:22.000 --> 30:23.180
She'll never be old enough
to understand.

30:23.180 --> 30:24.450
Every child has a right

30:24.450 --> 30:25.770
- to their own story.
- Yeah?

30:25.770 --> 30:27.340
Even if that story
is complicated.

30:27.340 --> 30:29.210
And what's your husband's
role in that story?

30:48.680 --> 30:50.560
I'd like for Nichole
to have this.

30:50.560 --> 30:52.310
This was a gift from my father,

30:52.310 --> 30:53.330
God rest his soul.

30:53.330 --> 30:54.890
I don't know what it is

30:54.890 --> 30:56.880
that you tell yourself

30:56.880 --> 30:58.840
so that, you know,
you can sleep at night,

30:58.840 --> 31:00.680
but Nichole is gonna know

31:00.680 --> 31:02.770
exactly where she came from,

31:02.770 --> 31:06.040
and how brave her <i>mother</i> was

31:06.040 --> 31:07.450
for getting her here.

31:07.450 --> 31:09.450
That's her story.

31:09.450 --> 31:11.520
All right?

31:11.520 --> 31:13.790
You're never gonna be
anything to her.

31:18.870 --> 31:21.070
You wanna know
what I tell myself?

31:22.340 --> 31:24.350
That she was my miracle,

31:26.240 --> 31:28.250
and that I let her go.

31:31.040 --> 31:33.410
Because I wanted
a better life for her,

31:33.410 --> 31:35.540
and so did your wife.

31:35.540 --> 31:37.250
Okay?

31:37.250 --> 31:39.240
So.

31:39.240 --> 31:42.060
If you can't honor
my wishes then...

31:42.060 --> 31:43.270
honor hers.

31:44.440 --> 31:47.250
Please, give this to Nichole,

31:47.250 --> 31:49.480
and let her draw
her own conclusions.

31:52.050 --> 31:54.490
You need to understand
that I protected your wife.

32:00.890 --> 32:02.540
What did you say?

32:04.700 --> 32:05.740
You what?

32:05.740 --> 32:07.490
I'm sorry,
but we need to wrap this up.

32:07.490 --> 32:08.880
Good.

32:11.250 --> 32:13.250
Yeah, good, good.

32:13.250 --> 32:15.500
Okay, I'll take it.

32:21.550 --> 32:22.560
Is there something

32:22.560 --> 32:24.580
you want me to tell your wife?

32:28.230 --> 32:30.180
No.

32:32.900 --> 32:34.940
I love you, my sweet girl.

32:38.240 --> 32:40.280
I love you so much.

32:41.440 --> 32:43.700
I love you.

32:45.680 --> 32:47.800
Do you wanna hold her?

32:49.210 --> 32:50.220
Yes, please.

32:56.660 --> 32:58.290
Oh, my baby girl.

33:00.530 --> 33:01.880
Hi.

33:01.880 --> 33:03.520
Oh, oh!

33:26.360 --> 33:28.360
You don't have to change back.

33:28.360 --> 33:30.630
My offer still stands.

33:30.630 --> 33:32.040
Treason and coconuts.

33:33.670 --> 33:36.660
I only have one home,
Mr. Tuello.

33:36.660 --> 33:38.710
You understand that, don't you?

33:38.710 --> 33:41.100
Yes.

33:41.100 --> 33:43.750
I used to live in Atlanta.

33:43.750 --> 33:46.000
Well, I hope you
get back there someday.

34:20.719 --> 34:21.860
<i>Gilead Ground.</i>

34:21.860 --> 34:24.750
<i>Airbus 3-0-0 Echo-Romeo-8-0.</i>

34:24.750 --> 34:27.719
<i>Request Taxi 33
for departure to Boston.</i>

34:27.719 --> 34:30.139
<i>Airbus 3-0-0 Echo-Romeo-8-0.</i>

34:30.139 --> 34:32.150
<i>Cleared for takeoff.</i>

35:33.040 --> 35:36.860
<i>♪ Oh, I can't take
another heartache ♪</i>

35:36.860 --> 35:39.050
<i>♪ Though you say
you're my friend ♪</i>

35:39.050 --> 35:41.470
<i>♪ I'm at my wits' end ♪</i>

35:41.470 --> 35:44.040
<i>♪ You say your love
is bona fide ♪</i>

35:44.040 --> 35:47.050
<i>♪ But that
don't coincide ♪</i>

35:47.050 --> 35:49.240
<i>♪ With the things
that you do ♪</i>

35:49.240 --> 35:51.440
<i>♪ And when
I ask you ♪</i>

35:51.440 --> 35:54.470
<i>♪ To be nice,
you say ♪</i>

35:54.470 --> 35:55.660
<i>♪ You've gotta be ♪</i>

35:55.660 --> 35:57.380
<i>♪ Cruel to be kind ♪</i>

35:57.380 --> 35:59.250
<i>♪ In the right measure ♪</i>

35:59.250 --> 36:00.880
<i>♪ Cruel to be kind ♪</i>

36:00.880 --> 36:02.620
<i>♪ It's a very good sign ♪</i>

36:02.620 --> 36:06.660
<i>♪ Cruel to be kind
means that I love you ♪</i>

36:06.660 --> 36:07.670
<i>♪ Baby ♪</i>

36:07.670 --> 36:08.700
<i>♪ Baby ♪</i>

36:08.700 --> 36:10.250
<i>♪ You've gotta
be cruel ♪</i>

36:10.250 --> 36:12.050
<i>♪ You've gotta
be cruel to be kind ♪</i>

36:12.050 --> 36:13.790
Thank you for
looking out for her.

36:18.670 --> 36:20.670
<i>♪ Well,
I do my best ♪</i>

36:20.670 --> 36:22.650
<i>♪ To understand,
dear ♪</i>

36:22.650 --> 36:24.680
<i>♪ But you
still mystify ♪</i>

36:24.680 --> 36:27.130
<i>♪ And I want
to know why ♪</i>

36:29.290 --> 36:30.300
Well?

36:31.890 --> 36:33.910
She was perfect.

36:37.250 --> 36:39.360
And now it's over.

36:54.430 --> 36:56.780
It doesn't have to be.

37:06.050 --> 37:07.650
<i>Please have your groceries ready</i>

37:07.650 --> 37:09.940
<i>for checking out.
Go in grace.</i>

37:10.880 --> 37:12.540
What do you want?

37:14.820 --> 37:17.420
Ready to jet.
You?

37:18.430 --> 37:20.060
Yes.

37:28.970 --> 37:30.250
I'm...

37:30.250 --> 37:32.280
not myself today.

37:34.440 --> 37:36.440
I didn't mean to snap at you.

37:39.750 --> 37:40.840
I'm late.

37:49.470 --> 37:51.500
You're with child.

37:56.250 --> 37:59.680
May God bless you
and bring forth this miracle.

37:59.680 --> 38:02.040
Yes.

38:02.040 --> 38:03.870
May He make me truly worthy.

38:05.250 --> 38:06.850
Again.

38:08.040 --> 38:09.080
Yes.

38:10.410 --> 38:13.060
Your Commander must be pleased?

38:14.880 --> 38:16.450
I haven't told him yet.

38:17.450 --> 38:18.850
Not with everyone so concerned

38:18.850 --> 38:20.060
over baby Nichole.

38:20.060 --> 38:22.640
There hasn't been a moment.

38:26.800 --> 38:29.410
I'm glad she's safe.

38:31.570 --> 38:33.220
Your husband, too.

38:34.970 --> 38:36.610
Thanks.

38:40.230 --> 38:42.140
You, too.

38:44.050 --> 38:47.100
I really think
everything's gonna be okay.

39:03.130 --> 39:04.790
Ofjoseph.

39:07.100 --> 39:09.290
Please come with me.

40:32.860 --> 40:38.000
<i>♪ Ah-ha ♪
♪ Ah-ha ♪</i>

40:38.000 --> 40:43.030
<i>♪ You've got
a cute way of talking ♪</i>

40:43.030 --> 40:45.640
<i>♪ You got
the better of me ♪</i>

40:51.440 --> 40:53.450
<i>Luke.</i>

40:55.440 --> 40:57.130
<i>Hi.</i>

40:58.580 --> 41:00.240
This is so weird.

41:02.890 --> 41:04.710
And I'm sorry.

41:05.680 --> 41:07.060
I'm sorry about that.

41:08.030 --> 41:10.330
<i>But...</i>

41:10.330 --> 41:12.520
<i>there are some things
that I need to tell you</i>

41:12.520 --> 41:14.240
<i>that I couldn't...</i>

41:14.240 --> 41:15.920
<i>before.</i>

41:18.030 --> 41:20.200
I can't imagine

41:20.200 --> 41:22.440
what you thought when you met...

41:22.440 --> 41:24.430
Nichole.

41:25.270 --> 41:28.210
<i>But you were probably
thinking a lot less</i>

41:28.210 --> 41:31.280
<i>about her journey
across the border</i>

41:31.280 --> 41:35.150
<i>and more about her journey
into the world.</i>

41:38.950 --> 41:42.830
It's not easy
to tell you this...

41:47.330 --> 41:49.350
'cause I am ashamed.

41:52.650 --> 41:56.340
<i>I had to build a life here.</i>

41:57.710 --> 41:59.840
<i>Of a sort.</i>

41:59.840 --> 42:00.850
<i>And you should, too.</i>

42:00.850 --> 42:02.710
<i>You deserve a life,</i>

42:02.710 --> 42:05.690
<i>a full life, Luke.</i>

42:05.690 --> 42:07.710
You deserve love.

42:10.290 --> 42:12.300
And you'll always have...

42:13.520 --> 42:15.190
You'll always have mine but...

42:16.660 --> 42:18.450
<i>I understand if...</i>

42:18.450 --> 42:22.230
<i>you maybe need more than that.</i>

42:25.860 --> 42:28.110
I need you to know
that Nichole...

42:30.110 --> 42:32.830
She was born out of love.

42:37.050 --> 42:39.460
<i>Her real name's Holly.</i>

42:41.280 --> 42:42.930
And her...

42:45.190 --> 42:46.420
Her father is a driver

42:46.420 --> 42:47.920
named Nick.

42:48.760 --> 42:50.780
<i>You met him.</i>

42:52.130 --> 42:55.000
He helped me

42:55.000 --> 42:56.430
to survive.

43:01.600 --> 43:04.130
<i>I</i> need <i>to believe that you</i>

43:04.130 --> 43:06.130
<i>can forgive me.</i>

43:08.880 --> 43:11.530
<i>I'm not the woman you remember.</i>

43:13.580 --> 43:16.120
<i>She's part of me.</i>

43:16.120 --> 43:17.660
<i>But I'm doing what I need to,</i>

43:17.660 --> 43:19.080
<i>to survive.</i>

43:20.440 --> 43:22.390
<i>You should, too.</i>

43:23.390 --> 43:25.390
<i>No, you...</i>

43:25.390 --> 43:27.260
<i>You have to.</i>

43:27.260 --> 43:29.720
<i>You have to for Hannah.</i>

43:29.720 --> 43:31.950
<i>It's all for her, Luke.</i>

43:34.040 --> 43:35.660
<i>This is all for her.</i>

43:35.660 --> 43:38.850
<i>I promise you,</i>

43:38.850 --> 43:42.410
<i>I am trying to get to her.</i>

43:42.410 --> 43:44.950
<i>I promise.</i>

43:47.080 --> 43:48.900
I love you.

43:51.750 --> 43:54.460
<i>I love you.</i>

44:01.030 --> 44:03.040
Blessed day, dear.

44:05.830 --> 44:07.150
What's going on?

44:07.150 --> 44:09.180
Well, aren't you a Nosy Nellie?

44:15.840 --> 44:17.490
All right.

44:26.440 --> 44:27.800
All right.

44:28.870 --> 44:30.990
Over here, dear.

44:30.990 --> 44:33.030
Cloak and wings.

44:37.240 --> 44:38.700
Mmm.

44:38.700 --> 44:40.520
Dress and boots, too.

44:42.770 --> 44:44.560
Coming.

44:54.040 --> 44:56.060
Clock's ticking.

45:02.730 --> 45:05.060
Let's get a good look.

45:08.730 --> 45:10.290
Oh...

45:11.300 --> 45:12.660
Lucky girl.

45:45.590 --> 45:46.600
Serena.

45:49.940 --> 45:51.570
Serena!

45:52.650 --> 45:53.930
What did you do?

45:57.870 --> 45:59.500
Posture, dear.

46:01.450 --> 46:03.450
Don't think about being clever.

46:04.450 --> 46:06.470
There are consequences.

46:19.100 --> 46:21.470
Hey. Hey.
Hey, hey, hey.

46:24.830 --> 46:26.040
Hey!

46:26.040 --> 46:27.900
You gotta see this.

46:29.280 --> 46:31.680
<i>We have
taken the extraordinary step</i>

46:31.680 --> 46:33.940
<i>of addressing
the world directly.</i>

46:34.950 --> 46:36.470
<i>We...</i>

46:36.470 --> 46:38.840
<i>are a family in mourning.</i>

46:38.840 --> 46:40.450
<i>A family devastated</i>

46:40.450 --> 46:41.820
<i>by loss,</i>

46:41.820 --> 46:43.250
<i>desperate for help</i>

46:43.250 --> 46:44.420
<i>and answers.</i>

46:44.420 --> 46:46.450
And we make this request

46:46.450 --> 46:48.030
to the Canadian government

46:48.030 --> 46:50.700
in peace.

46:50.700 --> 46:52.270
Our beloved

46:52.270 --> 46:54.040
baby daughter,

46:54.040 --> 46:55.970
Nichole Waterford,

46:55.970 --> 46:58.320
was kidnapped by
a dangerous fugitive

46:58.320 --> 47:00.360
fleeing our country.

47:01.910 --> 47:03.930
Nichole belongs in Gilead.

47:06.550 --> 47:08.850
We miss her dearly.

47:08.850 --> 47:10.890
We just want her back.

47:12.350 --> 47:13.870
We expect

47:13.870 --> 47:16.460
the government's
<i>full</i> cooperation,

47:17.460 --> 47:18.860
as our daughter

47:18.860 --> 47:21.360
is an innocent victim

47:21.360 --> 47:23.390
with no voice of her own.

47:25.730 --> 47:27.740
This is a family matter.

47:28.850 --> 47:32.410
You can help to keep it this way

47:32.410 --> 47:34.420
by sending her back to us...

47:35.650 --> 47:37.310
...safely.

47:47.870 --> 47:49.500
<i>♪ Yeah! ♪</i>

